G1 Z27.9 F720 ; Move print head up
G1 X0 Y200 F3600 ; park
G1 Z75.9 F720 ; Move print head further up
G4 ; wait
M221 S100 ; reset flow
M900 K0 ; reset LA

M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 ; disable motors
M73 P100 R0
M73 Q100 S0
; filament used [mm] = 422.97
; filament used [cm3] = 1.02
; filament used [g] = 1.26
; filament cost = 0.04
; total filament used [g] = 1.26
; total filament cost = 0.04
; estimated printing time (normal mode) = 9m 9s
; estimated printing time (silent mode) = 9m 11s

